profile: Foley Mountain Mechanical is a heating and cooling contractor serving Westport, the Rideau Lakes, Kingston, Perth and surrounding communities with the expertise that comes from over 25 years experience. When you choose Foley Mountain Mechanical, you choose a full service heating, cooling and ventilation company. We offer: central heating and cooling, indoor air quality control, geothermal heating and cooling, radiant flooring, ductwork, chimney masonry, and general service and maintenance. In addition, we service all fuel types.
